# smoower name map for TodoApi — the unpacker / VS Code extension reads this to
# render long forms. Format: short,long,kind[,owner]
#
# Boundary names (types, columns) are ALSO pinned in compilable code (global using
# for types, [Col]/[JPN] for members), so those rows are recoverable from the code
# itself; this file is the consolidated index plus the internal-only names that have
# no compilable carrier. Enum TYPES are absent on purpose — never global-using'd
# (bad code: obscures switch/nameof). Enum values could be shortened via
# [JsonStringEnumMemberName], but the full type name dominates so it rarely pays.

# --- hot types (global using aliases; entity/DTO/service only) ---
TT,TodoTask,type
TL,TodoList,type
TD,TaskDto,type
LS,ListSummary,type
CTR,CreateTaskRequest,type
TDb,TodoDb,type
TSvc,TaskService,type

# --- entity properties (pinned with [Col]; DB schema unchanged) ---
LId,ListId,prop,TodoTask
DA,DueAt,prop,TodoTask
AID,AssigneeId,prop,TodoTask
CmA,CompletedAt,prop,TodoTask
RD,RecurrenceDays,prop,TodoTask
PTI,ParentTaskId,prop,TodoTask
CA,CreatedAt,prop,TodoTask;TodoList

# --- internal names (no attribute carrier; this file is their only record) ---
GW,GuardWipAsync,method,TaskService
NO,NextOccurrence,method,TaskService
